descriptionHtml:
📻 Free Radio - Live Radio Station

Do you want to be always up to date listening Froggy 98.1 for Android, Table, Smartphone or any smart device? Then this is the live radio application you are looking for.

You do not have to search the web, with our app you can listen to the Froggy 98.1 the best quality, always live and without your headphones!

Listen to breaking news, special broadcasts and shows.

Listen to this free live online radio application, The only and best online radio in the entire country.

👍 Radio App Features

Our Froggy 98.1 application has these wonderful features:

🎵🆔 You can observe the title of the Song and the Artist.
🎧 You can listen to the station by turning off the screen of your cell phone to save battery power.
📱 In screen lock mode, you will see the app as a notification indicating which station you are listening to.
💌 Optimized design for all versions of Android.
⏱ You can use the sleep timer function to be able to turn off when you want the application.
⏰ You can also set alarms in the Wake up Alarm section to get up in the morning listening to your favorite station.

👍 Listen and Enjoy

In the app Froggy 98.1 free you will have access to more stations with the best music, where you can discover new singers, bands, shows and much more:
• Froggy 101.7
• 107.3 HANK FM
• Cat Country 107.1
• 106.3 Chicago WSRB
• Magic 105.4 Fm
• WDAS Fm 105.3
• Wamo 100.1
• Waly 103.9
• KCRW Radio
• WNYC Radio
• KNON radio
• KFNS 590 The Fan
• K104 Radio
• SomaFM: Indie Pop Rocks!
• Jazz Cafe
• 94.5 The Answer
• WARM 106.9
• 106.9 Fayetteville NC
• 107.1 WIRX
• And many more

Listen to Froggy 98.1 wherever you want it to be : From the country you are in, this station will be broadcasting 24 hours a day: music, sports, news, news and opinion all in your hand With this application.

The application uses a Streaming that connected to the Internet plays the radio signal you want.

Available for mobile phones and Android tablets .

If you are a lover of these Radio, use our application, since it is simple to use, with only two screen touches you will be listening to your favorite Radio in the country.

In addition, you will find all the songs that you enjoy and many more so you can always be listening to your favorite station.

NON-OFFICIAL APP, we only facilitate the access to streaming that the owner of his rights offers online.

IT'S FREE - EASY TO USE - QUICK TO OPERATE

► Thank you for downloading this radio app for any smart device, we hope you like it.

► If you have any questions, suggestions or questions just contact us.

⚠ Note: Internet connection required.

Attentive to any update we make to improve your experience.

If you want us to add any of your favorite stations, write us and we will add it as soon as possible.

🔁Feedback

😉 Our users are the most important for us and it shows in the feedback we have daily with them. Do not hesitate to contact us for any questions. We read all emails and reviews and answer all emails. We accept suggestions to add your favorite stations if we don't have them in our extensive list yet.

🔧 Support

We offer fast and reliable support to all users and we always answer the questions they write to us. If you have any problem with any of the stations, incompatibility with your device, etc., write to us and we will try to solve the problem as soon as possible.
